name: Kevin Wells
text: My daily cigarette stop is always a pleasure.

name: Mark Watson
text: Just off I-59 exit 188 at 4 way stop at intersection of hwy 202 and US 11. Open till 10 pm with plenty of room to fuel up with gasoline, diesel fuel or for the vehicles that are designed for flex fuel they have that too. Inside you will find a wide selection of snacks and beverages to make the road ahead a little more accommodating.

name: Scott Moyers
text: Awesome Prices Great Rewards Awesome Customer Service

name: Mark Watson
text: Conveniently located on US hwy 11 and just a few hundred yards of of I 59 at exit 188. Whether you need gas, diesel or maybe coffee and a snack this is the place to go. Pizza and other menu items prepared daily and of course you can also order your pizza to carry out.

name: Laura Smith
text: Opens early enough (5 a.m.)for me to stop omw to work so I give it 5 stars bc there aren't many places open this early.
